      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments conducted on geometrically similar pump at overlapping operating conditions with COU flow-speed envelope.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry at flow rates 2–6 L/min and speeds 2500–3500 RPM, fully encompassing the COU operating envelope. Geometric similarity confirmed via scaled impeller dimensions."
    },
    {
