    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 V&V 40 factors for MRL 2. Seven factors were formally assessed; six were scoped out as not required at MRL 2 with medium model influence. The overall credibility evidence was judged sufficient to support the regulatory submission. The discretization error factor showed GCI values marginally exceeding the 5% target at high-speed operating points; the team determined that the trend-identification purpose of the model was not materially compromised and accepted the submission on this basis.",
